Composed by Maiden Sano Otogami on parting with Nakatomi Yakamori, her lover, who was being sent into exile

あなたが行く長い道のりを、たぐり寄せて畳んで焼き尽くしてしまうような天の火が欲しいものだ
I wish I had the fire of heaven with which I could haul in, fold up, and burn away the long road that you must go.


